                        "subtype": "action_type",
                        "name": "One Action"
                    },
                    "frequency": "once per day",
                    "effect": "You raise *Lamentation of the Faithless* high above the battlefield, presenting its terrible glory for all to witness. All creatures within 60 feet that are able to see the sword must attempt a DC 50 Will save. Creatures with the unholy trait are immune to this effect, but creatures with the holy trait take a \u20132 status penalty on this save.",
                    "links": [
                        {
